  "signal_description": "The query retrieves the month when an issue is closed and the number of cases that are closed in each month. It is performed on the 'defaultview-217' table. The 'DATE_TRUNC' function is used to truncate the timestamp to the month level. The 'FIRST' function is used to select the first 'end_time' value where the 'event_name' is 'Change Status to Closed'. The 'COUNT' function is used to count the number of 'case_id' values where the 'event_name' matches 'Change Status to Closed'. The results are grouped by the first column and ordered by the first column."
